      <title>摩根大通优先股发售引发人们对优惠券的疯狂追逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-s-preferred-stock-sale-fuels-frenzied-hunt-for-coupons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通本周发行了大额优先股，销售部门因此全力以赴。他们的宣传很简单：大幅提高票息——这使得初级证券成为信贷领域最热门的交易之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-s-preferred-stock-sale-fuels-frenzied-hunt-for-coupons</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
