    <item>
      <title>南非电力公司停电威胁重现，兰特和债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/rand-and-bonds-fall-as-specter-of-eskom-blackouts-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国有电力公司警告称，可能会在 10 个多月内首次实施断电，这意味着南非这个努力摆脱多年停滞的经济将遭受打击，随后南非兰特和政府债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/rand-and-bonds-fall-as-specter-of-eskom-blackouts-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行通过外汇掉期注入 51 亿美元以缓解现金短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/india-rbi-injects-5-10-billion-via-fx-swap-to-ease-cash-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行通过外汇互换拍卖注入 51 亿美元，这是五年来首次使用该工具来缓解困扰金融系统的严重现金短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/india-rbi-injects-5-10-billion-via-fx-swap-to-ease-cash-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:22:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非电力公司警告称，电力故障可能造成断电风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eskom-warns-of-south-africa-power-cuts-as-it-depletes-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司表示，多座发电厂发生故障后，停电风险“很高”，可能结束连续 10 个月的稳定电力供应。兰特走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eskom-warns-of-south-africa-power-cuts-as-it-depletes-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 08:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德股价从 40% 的暴跌中恢复还有很长的路要走</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/novo-nordisk-shares-still-have-a-long-road-back-from-40-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，诺和诺德公司的一款减肥药的试验结果为投资者带来了急需的提振。但要想挽回过去六个月的跌势，还有很长的路要走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/novo-nordisk-shares-still-have-a-long-road-back-from-40-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
